{
  "number": 352,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/352",
  "title": "Wrap the searchBox input in a BEM div",
  "body": "I'm currently trying to replicate our magento styling into its own theme. Here is the current searchBox on Magento.\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/283419/10729399/312de402-7be9-11e5-91ee-149faa05d6b6.png)\n\nI wanted to add the small magnifying glass using `:after` pseudo-element, but it is not available on `input` elements.\n\nI suggest we always wrap the `searchBox` inside its own `<div class=\"ais-search-box\">`, so styling is made easier (and is more consistent with our other widgets).\n\nWDYT?\n",
